masks-newgeneration-unofficial.callerQuote: "The MegaShip fulfillment center is on fire! Third shift was still working—I got out but others are trapped in the back! There's millions of dollars in presents in there but honestly I don't care about that—PEOPLE are in there! The smoke is so thick!"
masks-newgeneration-unofficial.requirementsText:
• Rescue trapped workers from the burning warehouse
  • Help firefighters contain the blaze
  • If possible, save the presents—but lives come first
